OL,6,FTwo men jailed on the word of a
OL,7,Fcorrupt police officer with a history
OL,8,Fof racism have been posthumously
OL,9,Fcleared at the Court of Appeal.
OL,11,FBritish Rail workers Basil Peterkin
OL,12,Fand Saliah Mehmet died with
OL,13,Fconvictions after British Transport
OL,14,FPolice officer Detective Sergeant
OL,15,FDerek Ridgewell accused them of theft
OL,16,Ffrom a site he later admitted stealing
OL,17,Ffrom.
