OL,4,Cpolice officer posthumously cleared
OL,6,FTheir convictions were quashed by
OL,7,Fappeal court judges at a hearing in
OL,8,FLondon on Thursday, after the men's
OL,9,Fcases were referred by the body which
OL,10,Finvestigates miscarriages of justice,
OL,11,Fthe Criminal Cases Review Commission
OL,12,F(CCRC).
OL,14,FRidgewell, was involved in a number of
OL,15,Fhigh-profile and controversial cases
OL,16,Fin the early 1970s.
OL,18,FThe CCRC previously said it has
OL,19,Freferred 11 cases which relied on his
OL,20,Fevidence.
