OL,4,Cpolice officer posthumously cleared
OL,6,FHe died of a heart attack in prison in
OL,7,F1982 at the age of 37.
OL,9,FMr Mehmet, who died in 2021, and Mr
OL,10,FPeterkin, who died in 1991, were both
OL,11,Fsentenced to nine months in prison in
OL,12,F1977, over the theft of parcels from
OL,13,Fthe Bricklayers Arms goods depot in
OL,14,Fsouth London, where they worked.
OL,16,FThey said the items found in their
OL,17,Fpossession had been planted, and that
OL,18,Fany admissions said to have been made
OL,19,Fby them had been fabricated by the
OL,20,Fpolice.
