OL,6,FIn 1980, Ridgewell was jailed for
OL,7,Fseven years for stealing property
OL,8,Fworth #364,000 from the same site,
OL,9,Fwhile two of his colleagues were
OL,10,Fsentenced to six and two years,
OL,11,Frespectively.
OL,13,FThe CCRC previously said it has been
OL,14,Finvestigating the "historical racist
OL,15,Fand corrupt practices" of Ridgewell,
OL,16,Fwhose corruption has led to the
OL,17,Fconvictions of members of the so-
OL,18,Fcalled Oval Four and Stockwell Six
OL,19,Fbeing overturned in recent years.
