OL,6,FNine other convictions relating to
OL,7,FRidgewell have previously been quashed.
OL,9,FITV London News approached the British
OL,10,FTransport Police for a comment, Chief
OL,11,FConstable Lucy D'Orsi, said: "My
OL,12,Fcolleagues and I are profoundly sorry
OL,13,Fto all those affected by DS
OL,14,FRidgewell's atrocious actions and the
OL,15,Ftrauma that victims and their families
OL,16,Fsuffered as a result.
