OL,6,F"The identification of DS Ridgewell's
OL,7,Fvictims has always been important to
OL,8,Fus and we are pleased that the
OL,9,FCriminal Cases Review Commission have
OL,10,Fidentified two further victims.
OL,12,F"We continue to encourage any possible
OL,13,Fvictim or their family to reach out if
OL,14,Fthey feel they have been subject to a
OL,15,Fmiscarriage of justice."
